doc.after: Two feature length documentaries about the world of nerdcore hip hop were completed in early 2008 Nerdcore Rising and Nerdcore For Life Nerdcore Rising directed by New York filmmakers Negin Farsad and Kimmy Gatewood follows nerdcore pioneer MC Frontalot as he embarked on his first US tour in 2006 11 Nerdcore For Life by Chicago director Dan Lamoureux examines the genre as a whole and contains appearances by over three dozen of the best known performers in the scene 12
